wmsLayer.title: GA0340 a5 2m
wmsLayer.description: This layer is a bathymetry grid of survey area A5 from marine survey GA0340, collected on the Leveque Shelf, Western Australia. A total of six areas were surveyed and gridded at two metre resolution. The colour ramp for the WMS is stretched between 65-105 metres water depth. The dataset can be downloaded at the following URL http://services.ga.gov.au/metadata-gateway/metadata/record/79576.
